snippet.title: Makaimura Gaiden: The Demon Darkness (J; T+Eng) [GB]
snippet.description:
Real-Time playthrough
No cheats
No save states
This is a port of Garoyle's Quest II from NES. The game was released in Japan only in 1993. But there is fan-translation (by bailli) in the internet.
